These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Cigar: alhambra, siglo, baccarat, prince
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Cigar:baccarat##1
2. Cigar:alhambra is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Cigar:prince is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Cigar:alhambra is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Cigar   | alhambra | siglo | prince | baccarat |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Flower: zinnia, lily, marigold, balloon-flower
Nationality: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. Flower:lily is on the left of Flower:balloon-flower##1
2. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:french == Flower:zinnia##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
6. Nationality:french == Flower:zinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | marigold | zinnia  | lily  | balloon-flower |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
Music-Genre: metal, disco, funk, house
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of Music-Genre:house##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. Music-Genre:house is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. Music-Genre:house is on the right of Music-Genre:funk##1
5. Music-Genre:metal is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | house     | metal | disco |

