.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Transport: jet-ski, skateboard, subway, boat
Nationality: american, australian, indian, russian
1. Transport:subway is on the right of Nationality:russian##1
2. Nationality:australian == Transport:boat##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Transport:jet-ski##1
4. Transport:skateboard is on the far left##1
5. Transport:subway is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Transport   | skateboard  | jet-ski    | subway   | boat       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

