2. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Music-Genre:d&b##1
3. Movie-Genre:epic is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left of Movie-Genre:animation##1
5. Music-Genre:techno is on the left or right of Music-Genre:r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | d&b     | r&b  | techno  |

