3. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:disco and Food:banana##2
4. Food:artichoke is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco##3
6. Food:lime is on the left or right of Music-Genre:dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Food      | lime       | banana   | artichoke | papaya |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

