2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
4. City:edinburgh is on the left of City:san-francisco##1
5. City:san-francisco is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. City:edinburgh is in an even position##4
7. City:boston == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| City       | marseilles  | edinburgh | san-francisco | boston  |

